Ginger Gin Fizz
Ingredients
Thinly sliced ginger â€“ 3 to 4 slices
50ml Gordons gin
Dash of Angostura Bitters
Ginger ale
2 teaspoons of caster sugar
2 squeezes of lemon

Method
Slightly bruise the sliced ginger in the bottom of a highball glass (you can use the end of a rolling pin)
Add your gin and sugar
Mix with the ginger
Add lots of cubed ice
Add a dash of Angostura Bitters and 2 squeezes of lemon
Top up with ginger ale.
Garnish the cocktail with a slice of ginger or orange
